Global Variable# CGFLOAT_IS_DOUBLE

iOSiPadOSMac CatalystmacOStvOSvisionOSwatchOS

```
var CGFLOAT_IS_DOUBLE: Int32 { get }
```

## [Discussion](/documentation/corefoundation/cgfloat_is_double#Discussion)

Indicates whether [`CGFloat`](/documentation/corefoundation/cgfloat-swift.struct) is defined as a `float` or `double` type.
